CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 11, 1961, pg. 17 reads: "Stoop 'N' Bend Garden Club gave a very charming and gay Valentine dinner party at Loendi Club recently, to entertain husbands and a few friends. Members wore their prettiest dinner gowns to make the scene sparkle.  Above are officers Mmes. Rodney Pryor, Charles Waters Jr., Charles B. Adams, Harold R. Stoner and Herbert L. Simmons.  Out-of-town guest was Mrs. Sylvester Jones of Louisville, Ky., house guest of Mr. and Mrs. Leonard Hardy. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Stoop 'N' Bend Garden Club officers Mrs. Rodney Pryor, Mrs. Charles Waters Jr., Mrs. Charles B. Adams, Mrs. Harold R. Stoner, and Mrs. Herbert L. Simmons, posed behind table in Loendi Club for Valentine dinner party
